cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the remote S port for data to 2153 instead of 2152 prevents the CU from connecting to the DU's F1-U interface, leading to user plane data transmission failure.

du.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
du.explanation_en: Setting the remote N port for data to 2153 causes the DU to attempt connection on a mismatched port, disrupting F1-U interface communication.
